			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1441218">
									

<p>I would like to see such a thing as well.</p>
<p>Keeping in mind, of course, that some MTFs are hardass strike teams, ready for anything, and some (like &quot;Damn Feds&quot;) are more MiB types, fading into the background and pretending to be in charge of all sorts of civilian assets.</p>
<p>However, it would be very nice to have some guidance on, say, realistic size and equipment for the more combat-oriented MTFs, and maybe what we could expect Foundation guards to be equipped with as well. My military experience was in the Air Force - my unit wasn't prepared to kill less than several million people at a time, using ICBMs, so I can't draw on my past to fill in the gaps.</p>

